name: Congurbano Machines: Dungeon Workers
description:
Congurbano is a world in continuous motion. Under its surface fire, steel, electricity, and workers infuse life into this universe.

Part of the Congurbano Machines series: a happily dystopic universe.
Digital illustration, 300 dpi, 5777 x 3423  pixels
By Alejandro Burdisio (Burda)
